  "detailed_description": "<i>🏆 Winner of the Grand Jury Prize for Best VR Work at the 78th Venice International <br>Film Festival (2021)<br>🎞 Nominated for an Emmy Award in the Outstanding Interactive Media Innovation <br>category (2022) </i><br><br><strong>ABOUT GOLIATH</strong><br><br>Through mind-bending animation, <i>GOLIATH: PLAYING WITH REALITY</i> explores the <br>limits of reality and a true story of so-called ‘schizophrenia’ and the power of gaming <br>communities. <br><br>Echo (Tilda Swinton) guides you through the many realities of Goliath, a man who spent <br>years isolated in psychiatric institutions but finds connection in multiplayer games. <br>Combining heartfelt dialogue, mesmerising visuals and symbolic interactions, weave <br>through multiple worlds to uncover Goliath’s poignant story.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138380/extras/491f4ed2b65ecbfd2ba93fc3b342405b.poster.avif?t=1710869782\" width=560 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138380/extras/491f4ed2b65ecbfd2ba93fc3b342405b.webm?t=1710869782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138380/extras/491f4ed2b65ecbfd2ba93fc3b342405b.mp4?t=1710869782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138380/extras/ed614e8ed68c7ef6136f5a1e2d9464ca.poster.avif?t=1710869782\" width=560 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138380/extras/ed614e8ed68c7ef6136f5a1e2d9464ca.webm?t=1710869782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138380/extras/ed614e8ed68c7ef6136f5a1e2d9464ca.mp4?t=1710869782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138380/extras/f7234d363673704e730848c7f5375f08.poster.avif?t=1710869782\" width=560 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138380/extras/f7234d363673704e730848c7f5375f08.webm?t=1710869782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138380/extras/f7234d363673704e730848c7f5375f08.mp4?t=1710869782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Follow Goliath himself on his Twitch channel<br>Follow our Instagam for updates #goliathvr",
  "about_the_game": "<i>🏆 Winner of the Grand Jury Prize for Best VR Work at the 78th Venice International <br>Film Festival (2021)<br>🎞 Nominated for an Emmy Award in the Outstanding Interactive Media Innovation <br>category (2022) </i><br><br><strong>ABOUT GOLIATH</strong><br><br>Through mind-bending animation, <i>GOLIATH: PLAYING WITH REALITY</i> explores the <br>limits of reality and a true story of so-called ‘schizophrenia’ and the power of gaming <br>communities. <br><br>Echo (Tilda Swinton) guides you through the many realities of Goliath, a man who spent <br>years isolated in psychiatric institutions but finds connection in multiplayer games. <br>Combining heartfelt dialogue, mesmerising visuals and symbolic interactions, weave <br>through multiple worlds to uncover Goliath’s poignant story.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138380/extras/491f4ed2b65ecbfd2ba93fc3b342405b.poster.avif?t=1710869782\" width=560 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138380/extras/491f4ed2b65ecbfd2ba93fc3b342405b.webm?t=1710869782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138380/extras/491f4ed2b65ecbfd2ba93fc3b342405b.mp4?t=1710869782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138380/extras/ed614e8ed68c7ef6136f5a1e2d9464ca.poster.avif?t=1710869782\" width=560 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138380/extras/ed614e8ed68c7ef6136f5a1e2d9464ca.webm?t=1710869782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138380/extras/ed614e8ed68c7ef6136f5a